==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: difficult to move one tiny step.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: cùn bù nán xíng

===Idiom===
'''[[寸步]][[难]][[行]]'''

# cannot walk a step.
# difficult to move forward.

#: ''[[这]][[条]][[路]][[三]][[天]][[两]][[头]][[的]][[挖]],[[坑坑洞洞]][[的]],[[真]][[是]]'''寸步难行'''。''
#: ''[[政府]][[种种]][[严谨]][[的]][[法律]],[[使得]][[不肖]][[的]][[生意]][[人]],[[大叹]]'''寸步难行''',[[再]][[也]][[不能]][[任意]][[剥削]][[了]]。''

===Alternate forms===
[[寸步難行]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

